{"tid":2073073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好奇問一問? 點解班人大個個都好似神仙咁知道國安法內容?","createTime":"2020-06-21T05:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T07:32:45.000Z","uid":264426,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"23cf0a60d0a8e01172bea7c092ee9a952a3c6e6d","tid":2073073,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:11:02.000Z","msg":"明明係中央立法，個個親共派好似神仙轉世，知道哂佢內容係點?<br />\n<br />\n但係諗起之前譚耀宗做訪問話，佢自己都唔知國安法無端端黎左? 之後無啦啦話咩預左國安法黎，預左點立法?<br />\n<br />\n我搞唔清楚佢班友係點，咁其實佢地係知道國安法內容，定係係到猜黎猜去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前仲有有單好笑，唔知係咪譚耀宗，應該都係佢，話走去問中央國安法內容，但中央無同譚生講。<br />\n<br />\n屌，我真係好撚亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474ce0aeb0577de222af120736993ca4196204fa","tid":2073073,"uid":264426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:13:30.000Z","msg":"我睇翻譚耀宗訪問，真係笑到我仆街，心諗個個人大都唔知內容，而且人係香港，明明內容仲未完全知，但都可以噏到啲野出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916dc23ce4ea6958f1017c9505508cef19dcf9c6","tid":2073073,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:13:38.000Z","msg":"共狗嘅立場好簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oS2sBTDWkF4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoS2sBTDWkF4&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y2XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=bfccf032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oS2sBTDWkF4</a>"},{"pid":"d60b85999c21c93ea40c5441385b5a822688ce9a","tid"